*** Additional configs needed for D cloud 7.1 with XRd as PE nodes for Part 2 Lab Guide - L2VPN EVPN VPWS scenario  *** 



*** Configs needed on all PE nodes ( node-1,2,3,and 4 ) *** 


route-policy SET_COLOR_EVPN_VPWS
  pass
end-policy
!

router bgp 65000
 address-family l2vpn evpn
 !
 neighbor 198.19.2.11
  address-family l2vpn evpn
   route-policy SET_COLOR_EVPN_VPWS out
  !
 !
! 


** Config needed on PCE - 11 ** 


router bgp 65000
 address-family l2vpn evpn 
 !
 neighbor 198.19.1.1
  remote-as 65000
  update-source Loopback2
  address-family vpnv4 unicast
   route-reflector-client
  !
 !
 neighbor 198.19.1.2
  address-family l2vpn evpn
   route-reflector-client
  !
 !
 neighbor 198.19.1.3
  address-family l2vpn evpn
   route-reflector-client
  !
 !
 neighbor 198.19.1.4
  address-family l2vpn evpn
   route-reflector-client
  !
 !
